  "page": "A Song of Ice and Fire Campaign Guide",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #DEDEE2; text-align:center; font-style: italic;\"><i>A Song of Ice and Fire Campaign Guide</i></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Game-ASoIaF-campaignguide.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Game-ASoIaF-campaignguide.jpg\" src=\"/images/2/2b/Game-ASoIaF-campaignguide.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"323\" /></a><div>Cover</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Author</th><td>\nDavid Chart, Joshua J. Frost, Brian Kirby, Jon Leitheusser, Anthony Pryor, Robert J. Schwalb, and Owen K. C. Stephens</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Country</th><td>\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_States\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:United States\">United States</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Language</th><td>\nEnglish</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Series</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Roleplaying\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire Roleplaying\">A Song of Ice and Fire Roleplaying</a></i></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Genre(s)</th><td>\nFantasy</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Publisher</th><td>\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Green_Ronin_Publishing\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Green Ronin Publishing\">Green Ronin Publishing</a> (US)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Released</th><td>\nJuly 2010 (US)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Cover Artist</th><td>\nMichael Komarck</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Pages</th><td>\n251</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">ISBN</th><td>\nISBN 1-934547-13-1<br />ISBN-13 978-1934547-13-7</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Preceded&#160;by</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Roleplaying\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire Roleplaying\">A Song of Ice and Fire Roleplaying</a></i></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Followed&#160;by</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peril_at_King%27s_Landing&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Peril at King&#39;s Landing (page does not exist)\">Peril at King's Landing</a></i></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><i><b>A Song of Ice and Fire Campaign Guide</b></i> is a supplemental role-playing game book for use with <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Green_Ronin_Publishing\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Green Ronin Publishing\">Green Ronin Publishing</a>'s <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Roleplaying\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire Roleplaying\">A Song of Ice and Fire Roleplaying</a></i>, a role-playing game based on <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i>, the epic fantasy series by <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a>. <i>A Song of Ice and Fire Campaign Guide</i> describes Martin's <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a> in lavish detail, providing full details on all the major regions and principal players of the game of thrones.\n</p>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:ASOIAF\" title=\"Template:ASOIAF\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template_talk:ASOIAF\" title=\"Template talk:ASOIAF\"><span title=\"Discuss this te